welcome to my new project
i will discuss how to control climate change by using some specific tool 

We use our limited resources strategically to focus on protecting key species and ecosystems. 
For example, Mexico’s National Wetlands—which host 80% of the Pacific’s migratory birds and absorb twice as much carbon dioxide as a tropical forest of the same size.
We also bring legal, scientific, and technical support to communities. 
We strengthen their ability to fight industrial projects that damage their land, air, and water.

